eNCA speaks to Gauteng Police Commissioner, Elias Mawela. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Gauteng police are concerned about a spike in cash-in-transit heists. Provincial Commissioner, Elias Mawela, says it's worrying they are happening in broad daylight. READ: Cash-in-transit heists continue to spike But, he says police response efforts are getting better all the time. Watch the video above for more details